728025f-b.text:
Springfield Boulevard, near the S.E. corner of 116th Avenue, showing an old Hendrickson homestead. There were several Hendrickson farmhouses in the village of Springfield. The property was owned by N. Eromenacher in 1891 and by Florenoe C.
Saitn in 1918.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  1925
2-3) The same, at a later date.
P.L.Sperr  March 9, 1927
